# Project Setup Wizard

When a user requests to "set up a new project", "launch the setup guide", "create a new project", or similar, you MUST immediately use the AskQuestion tool to collect project configuration interactively via a modal UI.

## Trigger Phrases

Activate this wizard when user says:
- "Set up a new project"
- "Launch the setup guide"
- "Create a new project"
- "Start project setup"
- "I want to create a project"
- "New project"

